    "Adult_Dosing": {
      "text": "Complicated bacterial skin infections:\n4mg/kg q24h x7-14 days\nStaph bacteremia:\n6mg/kg IV q24h x2-6 wks\nRenal dosing\nCrCl <30, give q48h\nHD: give dose after dialysis, no supplement\nPD: no supplement",
